    "description": {
      "value": "<h2><span class=\"fontstyle0\">BRAINS AND GOOD LOOKS</span></h2>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Beginning when you choose this ladder at 1st level, you can always choose to use Intelligence instead of Wisdom for the Insight and Perception skills.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Additionally, after taking a long rest, if you wear no armor and wield no weapons, you gain a +2 bonus to Charisma or Intelligence (select one) until you make an attack roll or cast a spell. Select either Charisma or Intelligence as your primary born leader ability.</span></p>",
